modName: Start With Fus Ro Dah Level 1
summary: Do you keep remaking your character for one reason or another and hate to trudge through the main quests just to get Fus Ro Dah well this skips that annoyance.
descriptionHtml:
Level 1 Nord Male
Main quest line just completed the horn of Jurgen windcaller
No side quests complete (the golden claw is in my inventory)
No skills leveled up past starting levels
No script commands cheats or mods used
If you want to change character appearance name or race either one use the script commands or 
what i suggest option two
use this mod http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14152 there is a bathroom in the living quarters that allows you to completely re do character creation

I did this for myself because i keep restarting after a few hours and then trudge through the main quests for the like 13th time,thought i`d put it here just in case anyone else has this habit
author: Kckill4
